You are

599
00:35:58,840 --> 00:35:59,880
such an odd creature.

600
00:36:00,520 --> 00:36:01,840
Unflappable in a late-night cemetery, yet

601
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,680
so easy to be frightened by small things.

602
00:36:04,240 --> 00:36:05,800
Yet, you showed no fear

603
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:08,720
to my ugly musk.

604
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,800
Because there's nothing to be afraid of.

605
00:36:11,200 --> 00:36:13,560
The cemetery is the resting place of

606
00:36:13,560 --> 00:36:14,840
my dearest mother.

607
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:16,640
And you...

608
00:36:17,040 --> 00:36:18,440
you're wearing a mask

609
00:36:18,680 --> 00:36:20,320
to cover your birthmark.

610
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:21,800
Why should I be afraid of that?

611
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,160
Oh, right!

612
00:36:23,160 --> 00:36:24,280
I heard that

613
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:26,280
golden rings

614
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:27,840
could not remove

615
00:36:28,080 --> 00:36:29,520
one's birthmark.

616
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:31,160
You should stop using it.

617
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,360
It would be a pity

618
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,280
if the ring cut your face.

619
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:34,680
Why?

620
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:37,400
Are you taking your ring back?

621
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:39,840
No, you keep it.

622
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:43,000
If I can't get rid of those marks,

623
00:36:43,720 --> 00:36:45,480
I'll never get the nerve to

624
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,560
take off my mask in front of you.

625
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:48,760
Don't be.

626
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:50,600
It's not your fault.

627
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:53,240
Besides, one's character

628
00:36:53,240 --> 00:36:54,000
is never determined

629
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,600
by one's appearance.

630
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,320
I believe

631
00:36:57,480 --> 00:36:58,680
our appearance is

632
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,200
like

633
00:37:00,560 --> 00:37:01,560
makeup

634
00:37:01,560 --> 00:37:03,400
of actors and actresses.

635
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:06,480
It's only a small part of the character.

636
00:37:10,120 --> 00:37:11,760
Then, what do you think of me?

637
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:13,600
Am I virtuous?

638
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,320
Am I evil?

639
00:37:15,520 --> 00:37:16,560
Good or bad?

640
00:37:26,080 --> 00:37:26,920
I'll tell you

641
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:27,760
when you take off

642
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:28,680
your mask.

643
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:35,720
What if

644
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:38,680
you lose interest

645
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:40,760
in my appearance,

646
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:42,040
what should I do?

647
00:37:42,560 --> 00:37:43,840
Don't worry.

648
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,720
I gave you the ring in hopes of

649
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:47,960
helping you remove your birthmark.

650
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:49,520
But, I don't care

651
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:50,840
if you can remove it or not.

652
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:52,400
Because either way, I already

653
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:53,800
look you as a dear friend of mine.

654
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:55,840
I would never judge a book by its cover.

655
00:38:00,640 --> 00:38:01,440
Just, take it off.

656
00:38:04,240 --> 00:38:05,040
I will.

657
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:44,360
Lai Luozhi...

658
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:17,080
Lu Chuichui.

659
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:18,800
Today,

660
00:39:19,440 --> 00:39:20,960
I revealed my secret to you.

661
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,560
Whether you're frightened or not,

662
00:39:24,200 --> 00:39:25,920
please keep it for me.

663
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:27,720
Don't tell it

664
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:30,000
to another soul.

665
00:39:39,520 --> 00:39:40,760
Hope you can

666
00:39:42,040 --> 00:39:43,040
keep your promise.

667
00:39:49,520 --> 00:39:50,400
I believe you.

668
00:40:15,240 --> 00:40:16,160
What are you thinking?

669
00:40:18,320 --> 00:40:19,200
Nothing.

670
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:20,760
Well,

671
00:40:20,960 --> 00:40:21,840
look,

672
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:24,280
there are so many people here

673
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:24,960
all asking for

674
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:26,320
a perfect marriage.

675
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:29,920
You're here.

676
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:35,000
What a coincidence!

677
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:41,400
You're also here for a suitable match?

678
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:42,480
Why?

679
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,000
You don't think

680
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:44,440
you are the only ones who need it.

681
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:45,440
And people like us

682
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:46,800
shouldn't require a happy marriage?

683
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:48,280
Of course not.

684
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:49,760
I'm just saying,

685
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:51,120
how fascinating

686
00:40:51,240 --> 00:40:52,920
fate works.

687
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:54,080
Right, Xing?

688
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:02,320
Stop it.

689
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:03,720
Let's go.

690
00:41:03,880 --> 00:41:04,720
Where to?

691
00:41:08,080 --> 00:41:10,560
