692
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:11,280
Askin...

693
00:41:13,600 --> 00:41:15,160
Really?!

694
00:41:15,680 --> 00:41:16,960
You're also in want of a wife!

695
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:24,080
Who'd thought it!

696
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:26,800
Alright.

697
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:28,480
You are old enough

698
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:30,600
to take interest

699
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:31,800
in girls, not books.

700
00:41:31,920 --> 00:41:33,560
I'll go with you!

701
00:41:33,560 --> 00:41:34,600
Since you're interested, I'll do it

702
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:36,120
Xing,

703
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:38,560
you go talk with the general,

704
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,000
I'll be back soon.

705
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:41,680
Let's go.

706
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:45,240
I believe you rarely

707
00:41:45,240 --> 00:41:46,640
