00:42:06,560 --> 00:42:07,400
[Shen Du,]

712
00:42:07,720 --> 00:42:09,520
[you must drink it up.]

713
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:24,760
[Visiting the Temple for a new marriage?]

714
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,200
Jing Lin.

715
00:42:27,320 --> 00:42:28,120
Yes, sir.

716
00:42:45,440 --> 00:42:46,320
Xiangren.

717
00:42:47,680 --> 00:42:50,040
What are you trying to say?

718
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:54,560
Xing,

719
00:42:55,040 --> 00:42:56,240
I overheard Lu Chuichui

720
00:42:56,240 --> 00:42:58,640
