721
00:42:59,520 --> 00:43:00,800
[That's insane.]

722
00:43:01,040 --> 00:43:02,720
[How can a woman request a divorce?]

723
00:43:02,760 --> 00:43:04,200
[Why not?]

724
00:43:04,680 --> 00:43:05,840
The law says that

725
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:07,560
divorce due to

726
00:43:07,640 --> 00:43:08,680
disharmony

727
00:43:08,680 --> 00:43:11,160
does not require

728
00:43:11,200 --> 00:43:12,120
punishment.

729
00:43:13,840 --> 00:43:14,800
Besides,

730
00:43:15,080 --> 00:43:16,360
they've never...

731
00:43:17,080 --> 00:43:18,560
slept together.

732
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:20,760
They agreed to separate long ago.

733
00:43:21,080 --> 00:43:21,880
[Anyhow,]

734
00:43:21,920 --> 00:43:23,640
[I already told her]

735
00:43:23,760 --> 00:43:25,320
to find another one.

736
00:43:25,960 --> 00:43:26,880
But, it's a shame

737
00:43:26,920 --> 00:43:28,200
that there is no suitable man

738
00:43:28,320 --> 00:43:29,480
from your place

739
00:43:30,400 --> 00:43:31,960
and the Minstry of Justice.

740
00:43:32,040 --> 00:43:33,240
except for General Xu.

741
00:43:37,640 --> 00:43:39,720
Some day, I swear

742
00:43:39,760 --> 00:43:41,400
I'll shut Lu Chuichui up for good.

